The paper deals with deep learning-based approaches for natural image matting, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of affinity-based methods and contextual attention, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
